Main Screen
~~~~~~~~~~~

Through a gluster utility (check side-shell by pressing 'Alt-F2')
configure network, one can configure his network with the following
options.

http://www.gluster.org/images/screen-shots/new/misc/net-conf.png

''' dhcp method '''

Select the interface which needs to get IP using dhcp.

http://www.gluster.org/images/screen-shots/new/misc/net-conf-dhcp1.png

''' manual method '''

Select the interface which you need to configure manually.

http://www.gluster.org/images/screen-shots/new/misc/net-conf-manual1.png

[Modify] the pre-filled values, and [Apply] the changes.

http://www.gluster.org/images/screen-shots/new/misc/net-conf-manual2.png

